          <p class="text-xs text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">Flexible payment terms available. Contact us to discuss options tailored to your order volume.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="mt-5">
          <h5 class="text-white font-bold text-xs uppercase tracking-wider mb-3">Shipping</h5>
          <p class="text-xs text-slate-400 leading-relaxed">Sea freight and air freight available. DDP to USA, Canada, Mexico, LATAM, and Middle East.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Bottom Bar -->
  <div class="border-t border-slate-800">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-6 flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-3">
